member.name: ObjectType
member.summary: The ObjectType enumeration indicates the object type value of an EMF+ record.

member.name: ObjectType.ObjectTypeStringFormat
member.summary: Object type is a string format.

member.name: ObjectType.ObjectTypeImageAttributes
member.summary: Object type is an image attribute.

member.name: ObjectType.ObjectTypeCustomLineCap
member.summary: Object type is a custom line cap.

member.name: ObjectType.ObjectTypeMax
member.summary: Maximum enumeration value. Currently, it is ObjectTypeGraphics.

member.name: ObjectType.ObjectTypeMin
member.summary: Minimum enumeration value. Currently, it is ObjectTypeBrush.
